Package: vlc-plugin-vlsub
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, vlc (>= 1.1)
Description: VLC extension to download subtitles from opensubtitles.org
 Search and download subtitles from opensubtitles.org using the hash of the video currently playing or its title.
